name: Yatsuhashi (八橋Mix)
description:
A more refined MBW-COS Aurora_N dpep5mzpikaz+tmnd

This mix is intended to make cute and interesting dynamic images. It has a very cute and thick textural quality, like oil pastel, and uses a sort of art style reminiscent of ZUN or other similar artists, with simple faces and layered palette swatches for shading instead of detailed linework or gradients. The example images are similar to those in MBW-COS Aurora_N dpep5mzpikaz+tmnd. However, unlike that model you do not have to invoke any loras to get this textural quality effect. As such I consider Yatsuhashi a more complete version.

Because I believe in the open-source principles of Stable Diffusion, I always list the full merge recipe for any merge I make. I recommend other people to do so also. As Yatsuhashi is part of WagaShikashi collection, you can find the full merge recipe and ingredients details here:

https://huggingface.co/Jemnite/WagaShikashi
